WHERE archclie.cdente = archenti.cdente AND archenti.cdente =enteuniloc.cdente AND enteuniloc.cdunil = unitalocali.cdunil
archclie.cdazie = #cdazie:VARCHAR#
(archclie.cdagen = #cdagen:VARCHAR# OR archclie.cdsuba = #cdagen:VARCHAR#)
archclie.cdagen IN (SELECT cdagen FROM pgmr.archagen WHERE cdcapo = #cdcapoarea:VARCHAR#)
archclie.cdispe = #cdispe:VARCHAR#
enteuniloc.fseleg = #fseleg:VARCHAR#
upper(archenti.ragcog) LIKE upper(#ragcog:VARCHAR#)
archclie.fnoord = #fnoord:VARCHAR#
archclie.cdagen IN
#cdagenList[]#
sqlMap.select: SELECT COUNT(archclie.tkclie) FROM pgmr.archclie, pgmr.archenti , pgmr.enteuniloc, pgmr.unitalocali

SELECT archclie.tkclie, archclie.cdclie_m, archclie.fnoord, archenti.ragcog, unitalocali.indiri, unitalocali.comune FROM pgmr.archclie, pgmr.archenti , pgmr.enteuniloc, pgmr.unitalocali
order by $orderByClause$

SELECT clie.tkclie, clie.cdclie_m, clie.dsclie, clie.cdazie, clie.cddipa, clie.profil, clie.cdente, clie.fnospes, clie.dtfval, ente.ragcog, ente.ragnom, ente.cognom, ente.cdente, ente.cdfisc, ente.pariva, uloc.cdunil_m, uloc.cap, uloc.indiri, uloc.comune, uloc.cdprov, uloc.email, uloc.wwwpage, prov.cdprov, prov.cdprov_m, prov.dsprov, nazi.dsnazi, ugeo.lat, ugeo.lng, ugeo.rcode FROM pgmr.archenti ente , {oj pgmr.archclie clie left outer join pgmr.clieatti clai on clie.cdatti = clai.cdatti } , {oj pgmr.enteuniloc eulo left outer join pgmr.unitalocali uloc on eulo.cdunil = uloc.cdunil left outer join pgmr.nazioni nazi on uloc.cdnazi = nazi.cdnazi left outer join pgmr.province prov on uloc.cdprov = prov.cdprov_m left outer join pgmr.regioita regi on prov.cdregi = regi.cdregi left outer join pgmr.unitalocali_geo ugeo on uloc.cdunil = ugeo.cdunil } WHERE clie.cdente = ente.cdente and ente.cdente = eulo.cdente and clai.fgrivenditore = 'S'
clie.cdazie = #cdazie#
eulo.fseleg = #fseleg#
nazi.cdnazi = #cdnazi#
prov.cdprov_m = #cdprov_m#
regi.cdregi = #cdregi#
ORDER BY ente.ragcog, clie.dsclie
